        "localization": {
          "name": "Lightning Bearer",
          "description": "Enemy units that deal damage to this unit get stunned for 100TU, this is a Skin effect.\n\nHeals the user for 1% of total damage dealt. This unit is not affected by stun effects and cannot be sent to the reinforcements from the battlefield.\n\nGrants all enemies 3 Discharge Counters. Triggered both at the very start of the battle if this unit is on the battlefield, and when this unit enters the battlefield from reinforcements. Whenever an enemy enters the battlefield from reinforcements they will be granted 3 Discharge Counters. A unit can store a maximum of 3 Discharge Counters, and all are removed from a unit that leaves the battlefield.\n\nWhen this unit hits an enemy with any Discharge Counters with an attack, they will be stunned for:\n- 300TU if they have 3 Discharge Counters\n- 200TU if they have 2 Discharge Counters\n- 100TU if they have 1 Discharge Counter\nThen, the hit enemy will have 1 Discharge Counter removed."
        }
      }
